Easy Storage Cleaning Gadgets: Cleaning brush handle securely snaps into the pan, with its hanging loop and small size, storage on the wall, in closets, or under sink cabinets with ease. Slim and small sweeping sets easily fit into easy-to-reach places.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I love this dust pan & mini broom. I love that it comes with 2. So I can have one in the car and one in the house. The color is nice too. This has come in handy to clean up the little messes without the need to bring out all the other cleaning gadgets. It also has a self cleaner attached to the dust pan for the brush.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Handy little broom and dustpan set
reviews.reviewText: The broom and dustpan both work pretty darn well. They're a good size, too - small enough to be useful for tight spaces or small spills, but not comically small like others I've seen. I like that they even have a hair catcher on the dustpan. That's not something I've seen very commonly on smaller sets like this.Overall, it does exactly what it should, and it does it pretty well. The set is great, too - one for upstairs and one for downstairs. We're set!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality broom set!
reviews.reviewText: These are awesome room sets! My toddler can even use them to clean up his mess. The bristles are very strong and sweep up almost everything! Impressed with the quality of this.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great product affordable price

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality dust pan and brush set
reviews.reviewText: This dust pan set is good quality and seems very durable. It is a smaller than normal size but is not mini by no means. The brush has a silicone handle for a secure grip and has thick strong bristles that are very flexible. The dust pan is sturdy and has a flexible rubber edge to level it along the floor when sweeping dirt into the pan. A dust pan set always comes in handy especially the smaller sized ones like these and I find myself using them a lot even with handheld vacuums at my disposal. The bristles on the brush are heavy duty and would work great for even sweeping up sawdust and metal shavings, so it would work great in a workshop as well as in the house or for sweeping out a tent when camping. This is a great value for two sets of these and I recommend them to others.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I somehow thought the lip on them was silicone but it's just rubber. The brushes are a bit rough, not good for fine debris. Overall an ok set for rough cleanup but not as good as I was expecting. I'll be looking for another one that has fine bristles for fine dust pickup. Still not a bad product for the price, good to keep around the kitchen/garage/RV for general spills or quick cleanup between vacuuming. 3 stars for quality and at full list price I think they are over priced.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good value, comes in a set of 2!
reviews.reviewText: These set of portable dustpans is a great find on Amazon! It's a great value as it comes in a set of 2, and offers firm, sturdy bristles and a heavy duty dustpan. The pan is full-sized so it's made to pick-up big messes. The brush handle also has a sturdy loop so you can hang this in your utility closet.I always keep these kinds of portable dustpan with brush in the car. It's a staple to have and great for cleaning up messes like sand from the beach, Cheerios, and loose leaves and debris.The pack of two makes it great for both me and my husband's car. Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great little dust pan and brush set!
reviews.reviewText: It's hard to get enthusiastic about a dustpan and brush, but this set is as good as they come. It's solid and well-constructed. The brush is comfortable to hold onto and easy to sweep with. The dust pan is sturdy and not bendy like some of the cheaper ones I've had in the past. A set of two is great because we can keep one right next to the litter box and another with the cleaning supplies. The black and red colors are very attractive. Since you have to use dust pans, why not have a pretty set of them?
